And get this,  - Set vm.swappiness=1 — Kafka relies heavily on page cache; swapping kills throughput.

4
00:00:14,763 --> 00:00:20,815
Increase ulimit -n one lakh — Kafka opens many file descriptors.

5
00:00:20,815 --> 00:00:26,144
Use XFS or ext4 with noatime mount option.

6
00:00:26,144 --> 00:00:32,355
Allocate dedicated disks; avoid NAS/SAN for log directories.

